{"tid":1526003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「有片，外國文宣入」克警用警棍破壞私家車，今次比乜籍口","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:38:19.000Z","uid":194891,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"152a6138cd74ec7979f494a6a8f229fb4c16bac3","tid":1526003,"uid":194891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"內容：<br />\n借朋友AC放<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-gkiaASod8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-gkiaASod8w&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=72d65d1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-gkiaASod8w</a><br />\n<br />\n太子克警都可以9UP話用適當武力，或者生命受到威脅。<br />\n尋晚深夜睇蘋果直播見到呢一幕，D 防暴唔係以為警棍係對「路過車輛」的嘅「適當武力」吖馬，定以為警棍乜都整得停呀，同刑毀有乜分別，克警點解釋。<br />\n<br />\n如果換轉係市民咁敲警車，已經落車拔槍。<br />\n<br />\n無差別損壞無辜市民財產，如果對市民財產都咁「克制」，對性命安全又點。<br />\n<br />\n4點同我問爆佢!!!"},{"pid":"59ae66ecfa96dea3a10c61e87e468cc415b2ddca","tid":1526003,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=22a72b61\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\"